Development Stories:
mdrws
myqwDH


  Algorithm I - StemParser#parse:
    ☐ Takes an input word and parses it into a stem object
    ☐ Returns a list of 'candidate stems' for the unvocalized input word

  Algorithm II - StemCategorizer#categorize:
    ✔ Takes a stem object as input and returns a hash with the stem_category and stem_subcategory for conjugation @done (13-09-04 22:34)

  Algorithm III - StemConjugator#conjugate:
   ☐ Takes a stem object with the added virtual fields of 'categories' added onto it and returns a table of conjugations for the stem

  Algorithm IV - StemConjugator#match:
   ☐ Takes an input word, and a table of conjugations and matches it to the conjugations
   ☐ It alters the conjugation table to add a 'matched' flag when matching conjugations

Design Stories:
  ☐ Create an input text field that is optimized for entering arabic characters
  ☐ Create the arabic keyboard to drag from
  ☐ Drag short vowels onto the words
  ☐ Generate conjugation chart for verb

